    public class IGStaticValue
extends IGOperation
    This represents any constant value in the interpreter or ig
    Author:
    Guenter Bartsch Oct 2012, Valentin Tihhomirov converted conditional style into polymorphysm, http://codereview.stackexchange.com/questions/18016/replacing-conditional-with-polymorphysm-slows-down-the-performance
